{"tid":1185850,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"微電影《5月35日》劇情大綱","createTime":"2019-06-04T13:46:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-04T13:59:34.000Z","uid":222542,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"734e3b646ba635acdc43f7b1e7eaa96ec94f6615","tid":1185850,"uid":222542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T13:46:31.000Z","msg":"故事內容：<br />\n故事講述在「某事件」發生的5月35日當天，4名不同背景的年輕人之經歷。而片中到最後也沒有交代「某事件」到底是什麼。<br />\n<br />\n第一條線講述一個領袖，正在策劃一個大型活動。<br />\n<br />\n第二條線講述一個知識份子，因為睇左上述活動嘅單張，毅然決定參加活動。<br />\n<br />\n第三條線講緊一個讀工程嘅學生，因為無聊，所以當日都去咗食花生。<br />\n<br />\n第四條線講緊一個富二代，當日如常吃喝玩樂。<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n中間刪1萬字<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n<br />\n結局：<br />\n<br />\n領袖：死咗<br />\n知識份子：終日被打壓/迫害/囚禁<br />\n工程學生：成為工程師，過著一般人過的生活<br />\n富二代：如常吃喝玩樂"},{"pid":"a3052f40c0b661126f223bbfc5dc65e52186f8c9","tid":1185850,"uid":222542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T13:48:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BSSpYPs.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBSSpYPs.gif&h=88b0fdfb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"600169c914e4ce96cb1ef81e5cbb72ae366b0069","tid":1185850,"uid":222542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T13:59:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}